OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA few bright spells possible
OL,6,Fearly on, but cloud increasing through
OL,7,Fthe day. Largely dry through the
OL,8,Fafternoon with outbreaks of rain
OL,9,Freaching the far south of the region
OL,10,Ffrom late afternoon. Still warm and
OL,11,Fincreasingly humid.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FRain will continue to push
OL,14,Fnorthwards across the region. The rain
OL,15,Fwill become heavy and persistent at
OL,16,Ftimes, possibly thundery. Feeling
OL,17,Frather mild.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
